Retrieving OpenStreetMap data in XML by bounding box:
http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/API_v0.6#Retrieving_map_data_by_bounding_box:_GET_.2Fapi.2F0.6.2Fmap

http://api.openstreetmap.org/api/0.6/map?bbox=left,bottom, right,top

left is the longitude of the left (westernmost) side of the bounding box.
bottom is the latitude of the bottom (southernmost) side of the bounding box.
right is the longitude of the right (easternmost) side of the bounding box.
top is the latitude of the top (northernmost) side of the bounding box.


to get coordinates: http://www.getlatlon.com/

http://api.openstreetmap.org/api/0.6/map?bbox=4.331445693969727,50.8924225710247,4.347238540649414,50.899000134415864


Running Saxon:

java -jar ../saxon9he.jar -t -s:atomium.xml -xsl:maporizer.xsl -o:map.svg

